# Scenario

A user reported receiving an email claiming that their **Chase Bank account had been temporarily blocked due to unusual activities**.

The objective of this investigation was to determine whether the email was legitimate or malicious, identify Indicators of Compromise (IOCs), investigate the sender infrastructure, analyze embedded URLs, and provide a final incident report.

